{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be lively and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Legal Group</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #333333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #d32f2f; /* Deep Red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            margin: 5px 0 0;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #d32f2f;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #333333;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #d32f2f;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.7), rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/cccccc/ffffff?text=Professional+Image') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 25px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #fefefe;\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid #d32f2f;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n        .cta {\n            background-color: #d32f2f;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .cta h2 {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: #e0e0e0;\n            color: #c62828;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>APEX LEGAL GROUP</h1>\n        <p>Upholding Justice with Integrity and Expertise</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Our Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Your Trusted Legal Partners</h2>\n        <p>Dedicated to achieving the best outcomes for our clients.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Apex Legal Group</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">\n                At Apex Legal Group, we are more than just legal professionals; we are dedicated advocates committed to providing exceptional legal representation. Our firm is built on a foundation of rigorous research, strategic thinking, and an unwavering commitment to our clients' best interests. We pride ourselves on our ability to navigate complex legal landscapes with clarity and confidence, ensuring you receive the expert guidance you deserve.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Corporate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Assisting businesses with formation, contracts, compliance, and dispute resolution.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Criminal Defense</h3>\n                    <p>Vigorously defending your rights and freedoms in all criminal matters.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Family Law</h3>\n                    <p>Providing compassionate and effective representation for divorce, custody, and support.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Real Estate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Handling all aspects of property transactions and disputes with precision.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Personal Injury</h3>\n                    <p>Fighting for compensation for those injured due to negligence.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Intellectual Property</h3>\n                    <p>Protecting your innovations and creative works.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <div class=\"cta\">\n                <h2>Ready to Discuss Your Case?</h2>\n                <p>Let us help you navigate your legal challenges with confidence.</p>\n                <a href=\"mailto:info@apexlegal.com\" class=\"btn\">Contact Us Today</a>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Legal Group. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n        <p>123 Justice Lane, Law City, LC 45678 | Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}